The Level 1 suite is back to green, which confirms the runtime behavior. The last issue is purely a `happy-server` compile concern from pulling the entire `SyncNode` source just to reach the token schema, so I’m extracting that schema into its own shared file to keep both the server compile and the runtime path clean.
